            <code>abx-pkg</code> provides consistent interfaces for runtime
            dependency resolution &amp; installation across many package managers
            and OSs, built with <a href="https://pydantic-docs.helpmanual.io/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">pydantic</a>
            v2 for strong static typing and easy conversion to/from JSON. It's
            usable with <a href="https://docs.djangoproject.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Django</a>,
            <a href="https://django-ninja.dev/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">django-ninja</a>,
            and OpenAPI tools, and its driver layer can be
            <a href="https://github.com/pyinfra-dev/pyinfra" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">pyinfra</a>,
            <a href="https://github.com/ansible/ansible" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">ansible</a>,
            or the built-in <code>abx-pkg</code> engine.
          </p>
          <p>
